---
title: Cal Smart Dilly Double Turkey Burgers with Yogurt-Feta Sauce
description: Turkey patties get a fresh and zesty lift from lemons and sliced cucumbers while the feta-boosted tzatziki schmeared over top injects these burgers with briny goodness. A fresh side salad brightens things up for a light summer supper!
